data.description: Built in 2020, this exquisite “like new” smart home is a gem conveniently located within minutes of all things East Nashville has to offer. With modern design and impeccable craftsmanship, this home boasts stainless steel appliances, granite / marble countertops, hardwood floors, a large primary w/ en-suite bath and walk-in closet. Features include a spacious attached 2 car garage, covered private balcony off the main living area, fresh paint, updated landscaping, and exterior uplighting. This one won’t last long! Owner Occ-STR eligible.
